Eddie Jones (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eddie_Jones_(actor) 0 Eddie Jones (born 1937) is an American actor. He is known for playing Clark Kent's father Jonathan Kent in the ABC television series Lois Clark: The New Adventures of Superman, and Charles Borden (a.k.a. The Official), head of The Agency, in the sci-fi television series The Invisible Man. Eddie_Jones ( born 1937 ) is an_American_actor .
